window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>They say never make a deal with a demon…but what if I didn’t have a choice?</p> <p>On my 18th birthday, my soul was traded to three sin demons as payment for my foster-father’s gambling debts.</p> <p>Little did I know that being with them would unleash my own desires and hell on Earth.</p> <p>Literally.</p> <p>But these tempting devils aren’t the only ones with ungodly powers, because I’m no angel myself.</p> <p>My dark secret can end up destroying us all.</p> <p><i>Sin Demons</i> is a fiery paranormal romance series full of dominating hellions, gritty humor, underworld mystery, and a lost heroine embracing her faults to find her true power. This is a reverse harem/why choose series.</p> <p>This set includes the first three books in the Sin Demons Series—<i>Playing with Hellfire</i>, <i>Hell in a Handbasket</i>, and <i>All Shot to Hell</i>—plus exclusive bonus content and character illustrations.</p>"; 
